arison of our predictions of the CO$_2$ and CH$_4$ mole fractions in Lake\nVostok with future in situ measurements will allow disentangling between the\npossible supply sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2013 00:21:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
